		"Title": "Geleceğin Yapay Zeka ile Güçlendirilmiş Hastasını ve Doktorunu Tasarlamak",
		"Image": "",
		"Body": "<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\">Yapay zekayı zaten kullanılıyor ve sağlık hizmetlerinde büyük değişikliklere yol açıyor. Yapay zekanın sağlık sektöründe engellenemez ilerlemesine bakışımızın<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://news.lenovo.com/the-human-centric-rise-of-artificial-intelligence-in-healthcare/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">birinci b</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ö</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">l</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ü</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">m</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ü</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">nde</span></a>yapay zekanın teşhisleri, klinik altyapısını ve önleyici bakımı nasıl iyileştirdiğini keşfettik. Lenovo'nun hastane yönetiminden algoritma geliştirmeye her adımdaki rolü dahil olmak üzere<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://news.lenovo.com/envisioning-the-ai-empowered-patient-and-physician-of-the-future/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">tutumlar, d</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ü</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">zenlemeler ve temel teknolojiler </span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ü</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">zerine bir el kitab</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ı</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">n</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ı</span></a> inceleyerek işe başlayabilirsiniz.</p> \n<p style=\"margin-top: 12pt;\"><span>T</span><span>ü</span><span>m bu g</span><span>üç</span><span>l</span><span>ü</span><span> d</span><span>ö</span><span>n</span><span>üşü</span><span>m hem hastalar hem de sa</span><span>ğ</span><span>l</span><span>ı</span><span>k uzmanlar</span><span>ı</span><span> i</span><span>ç</span><span>in bir</span><span></span><em><span>ara</span></em><em><span>ç</span></em><span></span><span>g</span><span>ö</span><span>revi g</span><span>ö</span><span>r</span><span>ü</span><span>r ve bu e</span><span>ğ</span><span>ilim gelecek on y</span><span>ı</span><span>lda da artmaya devam edecektir. Peki yapay zekan</span><span>ı</span><span>n g</span><span>ü</span><span>venilir doktorlar</span><span>ı</span><span>n yerini almas</span><span>ı</span><span> zor g</span><span>ö</span><span>r</span><span>ü</span><span>n</span><span>ü</span><span>yorsa ve hasta verilerinin gizlili</span><span>ğ</span><span>ine uymas</span><span>ı</span><span> gerekiyorsa, ne de</span><span>ğ</span><span>i</span><span>ş</span><span>ecek?</span></p> \n<p><strong><span>Be</span></strong><strong><span>ş</span></strong><strong><span> Y</span></strong><strong><span>ı</span></strong><strong><span>l Sonra Yapay Zeka: Daha Ak</span></strong><strong><span>ı</span></strong><strong><span>ll</span></strong><strong><span>ı</span></strong><strong><span> Makineler ve Sanal Yard</span></strong><strong><span>ı</span></strong><strong><span>mc</span></strong><strong><span>ı</span></strong><strong><span>lar</span></strong></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>Be</span><span>ş</span><span> y</span><span>ı</span><span>l kadar ileri gidip bu alan</span><span>ı</span><span>n nas</span><span>ı</span><span>l de</span><span>ğ</span><span>i</span><span>ş</span><span>ebilece</span><span>ğ</span><span>ine bir bakal</span><span>ı</span><span>m. Teknolojideki her seferinde b</span><span>ü</span><span>y</span><span>ü</span><span>yen s</span><span>ıç</span><span>ramalar, yukar</span><span>ı</span><span>daki </span><span>ö</span><span>rneklerin yayg</span><span>ı</span><span>nl</span><span>ığı</span><span>n</span><span>ı</span><span> ve g</span><span>ü</span><span>c</span><span>ü</span><span>n</span><span>ü</span><span> art</span><span>ı</span><span>racakt</span><span>ı</span><span>r elbette ancak esas de</span><span>ğ</span><span>i</span><span>ş</span><span>iklik nerede olacak?</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in 0.0001pt;\"><span>Ak</span><span>ı</span><span>ll</span><span>ı</span><span> telefonunuzda bir sanal asistanla </span><span>ç</span><span>al</span><span>ışı</span><span>rken arka planda ne kadar i</span><span>ş</span><span> yap</span><span>ı</span><span>ld</span><span>ığı</span><span>n</span><span>ı</span><span> bir d</span><span>üşü</span><span>n</span><span>ü</span><span>n. <em>Sizin</em></span><span></span><span>sesinizi </span><span>öğ</span><span>renebilen ses tan</span><span>ı</span><span>ma </span><span>ö</span><span>zelli</span><span>ğ</span><span>inden canl</span><span>ı</span><span> arama sonu</span><span>ç</span><span>lar</span><span>ı</span><span>n</span><span>ı</span><span> taramaya, ge</span><span>ç</span><span>mi</span><span>ş</span><span> davran</span><span>ış</span><span>lardan yararlanmaya ve cihazlar aras</span><span>ı</span><span>nda sonu</span><span>ç</span><span>lar</span><span>ı</span><span> payla</span><span>ş</span><span>maya; b</span><span>ü</span><span>t</span><span>ü</span><span>n i</span><span>ş</span><span>lemler an</span><span>ı</span><span>nda olur ve </span><span>ç</span><span>o</span><span>ğ</span><span>umuz yapay zekan</span><span>ı</span><span>n bunu</span><span></span><em><span>nas</span></em><em><span>ı</span></em><em><span>l</span></em><span> yapabildi</span><span>ğ</span><span>ine kafa yormay</span><span>ı</span><span>z. Tease, te</span><span>ş</span><span>his teknolojisinde de benzer bir geli</span><span>ş</span><span>me olmas</span><span>ı</span><span>n</span><span>ı</span><span> bekliyor.</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>Lenovo'nun Y</span><span>ü</span><span>ksek Performansl</span><span>ı</span><span> Bilgi </span><span>İş</span><span>lem ve Yapay Zeka M</span><span>ü</span><span>d</span><span>ü</span><span>r</span><span>ü</span><span> Scott Tease, </span><span>“</span><span>PET taramas</span><span>ı</span><span> veya MRI i</span><span>ç</span><span>in hastaneye gitti</span><span>ğ</span><span>inizi d</span><span>üşü</span><span>n</span><span>ü</span><span>n,</span><span>”</span><span> diye anlat</span><span>ı</span><span>yor. </span><span>“</span><span>Doktor veya teknisyen g</span><span>ö</span><span>r</span><span>ü</span><span>nt</span><span>ü</span><span>leri incelemeden </span><span>ö</span><span>nce, bir algoritma verileri yorumluyor ve normal g</span><span>ö</span><span>r</span><span>ü</span><span>nmeyen her </span><span>ş</span><span>eyi i</span><span>ş</span><span>aretliyor. Bu, sa</span><span>ğ</span><span>l</span><span>ı</span><span>k </span><span>ç</span><span>al</span><span>ış</span><span>anlar</span><span>ı</span><span>n</span><span>ı</span><span>n i</span><span>ş</span><span>lerini h</span><span>ı</span><span>zland</span><span>ı</span><span>r</span><span>ı</span><span>r, dikkatlerini sorunlara </span><span>ç</span><span>eker ve hi</span><span>ç</span><span>bir </span><span>ş</span><span>eyin g</span><span>ö</span><span>z ard</span><span>ı</span><span> edilmemesini sa</span><span>ğ</span><span>lar.</span><span></span><span>Asl</span><span>ı</span><span>nda, bu s</span><span>ü</span><span>re</span><span>ç</span><span>ler </span><span>ş</span><span>u anda yetkililer taraf</span><span>ı</span><span>ndan inceleniyor.</span><span>”</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in; text-align: center;\"><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"assets/build-in-contents/images/AI1.jpg\" style=\"height: 317px; width: 600px;\"></span></p> \n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><span>Geli</span><span>ş</span><span>tirilmi</span><span>ş</span><span> </span><span>çö</span><span>z</span><span>ü</span><span>n</span><span>ü</span><span>rl</span><span>ü</span><span>k ve analizler, k</span><span>üçü</span><span>k ve </span><span>ö</span><span>rt</span><span>ü</span><span>k semptomlarda bile uzaktan tarama ve te</span><span>ş</span><span>his koyma se</span><span>ç</span><span>eneklerine olanak tan</span><span>ı</span><span>r.</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>Doktorlar bu yapay zeka kullan</span><span>ı</span><span>m</span><span>ı</span><span>n</span><span>ı</span><span> benimsemeye daha yatk</span><span>ı</span><span>n olabilir, ancak dev gibi b</span><span>ü</span><span>y</span><span>ü</span><span>yen izleme verileri ne olacak? Sa</span><span>ğ</span><span>l</span><span>ı</span><span>k takip cihazlar</span><span>ı</span><span>n</span><span>ı</span><span>n olas</span><span>ı</span><span> endi</span><span>ş</span><span>eleri olan kliniklere otomatik olarak ping atma olas</span><span>ı</span><span>l</span><span>ığı</span><span> pek ho</span><span>ş</span><span> kar</span><span>şı</span><span>lanm</span><span>ı</span><span>yor.</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>Lenovo'nun eski klinisyeni ve k</span><span>ü</span><span>resel sa</span><span>ğ</span><span>l</span><span>ı</span><span>k </span><span>ü</span><span>r</span><span>ü</span><span>nleri y</span><span>ö</span><span>neticisi Dr. Dan Stevens, </span><span>“</span><span>Uyar</span><span>ı</span><span>lar</span><span>ı</span><span>n yaratt</span><span>ığı</span><span> tela</span><span>ş</span><span> ger</span><span>ç</span><span>ekten endi</span><span>ş</span><span>e uyand</span><span>ı</span><span>r</span><span>ı</span><span>yor ve bu durumun yak</span><span>ı</span><span>nda de</span><span>ğ</span><span>i</span><span>ş</span><span>ece</span><span>ğ</span><span>ini zannetmiyorum,</span><span>”</span><span> diyor. </span><span>“</span><span>Muhtemelen, en az</span><span>ı</span><span>ndan k</span><span>ı</span><span>sa vadede, giyilebilir veriler, talep </span><span>ü</span><span>zerine kullan</span><span>ı</span><span>labilecek yararl</span><span>ı</span><span> bir te</span><span>ş</span><span>his deste</span><span>ğ</span><span>i sunacakt</span><span>ı</span><span>r.</span><span>”</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>Ayr</span><span>ı</span><span>ca, her </span><span>ş</span><span>eyin bir web sitesiyle veya uygulamayla parmaklar</span><span>ı</span><span>n</span><span>ı</span><span>z</span><span>ı</span><span>n ucuna gelebilmesini sa</span><span>ğ</span><span>layan </span><span>“</span><span>kolayl</span><span>ı</span><span>k</span><span>”</span><span> i</span><span>ç</span><span>in talebin artmas</span><span>ı</span><span> da m</span><span>ü</span><span>mk</span><span>ü</span><span>n. B</span><span>ö</span><span>ylece, yapay zeka bir dizi hedefli sorunun biyometri ile birlikte insanlar</span><span>ı</span><span>n do</span><span>ğ</span><span>ru bak</span><span>ı</span><span>ma ula</span><span>ş</span><span>mas</span><span>ı</span><span>na yard</span><span>ı</span><span>mc</span><span>ı</span><span> olaca</span><span>ğı</span><span> sohbet robotu usul</span><span>ü</span><span> bir doktor bak</span><span>ı</span><span>m</span><span>ı</span><span>na yol a</span><span>ç</span><span>abilir.</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>Telet</span><span>ı</span><span>p, elbette, y</span><span>ı</span><span>llar </span><span>ö</span><span>nce s</span><span>ı</span><span>cak evimizde otururken bir doktora dan</span><span>ış</span><span>may</span><span>ı</span><span> m</span><span>ü</span><span>mk</span><span>ü</span><span>n k</span><span>ı</span><span>ld</span><span>ı</span><span>; ancak elektronik bir doktor maliyeti </span><span>ç</span><span>ok b</span><span>ü</span><span>y</span><span>ü</span><span>k </span><span>ö</span><span>l</span><span>çü</span><span>de azaltabilir. </span><span>İ</span><span>nceleyip onaylamak i</span><span>ç</span><span>in ger</span><span>ç</span><span>ek bir insan devreye girse bile, yapay zeka liderli</span><span>ğ</span><span>indeki bir g</span><span>ö</span><span>r</span><span>üş</span><span>me ve veri de</span><span>ğ</span><span>erlendirmesi verimlili</span><span>ğ</span><span>i kesinlikle art</span><span>ı</span><span>racakt</span><span>ı</span><span>r.</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin-top: 12pt;\"><span>Stevens, </span><span>“</span><span>Yapay zeka ile te</span><span>ş</span><span>his karma</span><span>şı</span><span>k bir s</span><span>ü</span><span>re</span><span>ç</span><span>tir,</span><span>”</span><span> diyor. </span><span>“</span><span>Kolayl</span><span>ı</span><span>k, risk de</span><span>ğ</span><span>erlendirmesi ve do</span><span>ğ</span><span>ruluk, hepsi rol oynar. Sohbet robotu yakla</span><span>şı</span><span>m</span><span>ı</span><span>n</span><span>ı</span><span>n tehlikeli semptomlar</span><span>ı</span><span> olan herhangi bir </span><span>ş</span><span>eyin yerine ge</span><span>ç</span><span>ece</span><span>ğ</span><span>ini d</span><span>üşü</span><span>nm</span><span>ü</span><span>yoruz.</span><span>”</span></p> \n<p><strong><span>10 Y</span></strong><strong><span>ı</span></strong><strong><span>lda Yapay Zeka: Ki</span></strong><strong><span>ş</span></strong><strong><span>iselle</span></strong><strong><span>ş</span></strong><strong><span>tirilmi</span></strong><strong><span>ş</span></strong><strong><span>, K</span></strong><strong><span>ü</span></strong><strong><span>resel Eri</span></strong><strong><span>ş</span></strong><strong><span>imli T</span></strong><strong><span>ı</span></strong><strong><span>p</span></strong></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in 0.0001pt;\"><span>Buraya kadar </span><span>ö</span><span>zetlenen de</span><span>ğ</span><span>i</span><span>ş</span><span>ikliklerin, teknolojideki geli</span><span>ş</span><span>meler ve daha geni</span><span>ş</span><span> benimsenme sayesinde daha da ilerledi</span><span>ğ</span><span>ini d</span><span>üşü</span><span>n</span><span>ü</span><span>n.</span><span></span><span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://news.lenovo.com/debunking-misconceptions-about-ai/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">Yapay zeka ile ilgili yan</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ı</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">lg</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ı</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">lar</span></a></span><span></span><span>da zamanla ortadan kalkacak ve yapay zeka destekli teknolojinin ba</span><span>ş</span><span>ar</span><span>ı</span><span>yla da</span><span>ğı</span><span>t</span><span>ı</span><span>lmas</span><span>ı</span><span> halk</span><span>ı</span><span>n algoritmik ya</span><span>ş</span><span>ama daha </span><span>ç</span><span>ok g</span><span>ü</span><span>venmesini sa</span><span>ğ</span><span>layacakt</span><span>ı</span><span>r. </span><span>Ş</span><span>ehir sokaklar</span><span>ı</span><span>nda ve otoyollarda sorunsuz bir </span><span>ş</span><span>ekilde seyreden otonom ara</span><span>ç</span><span> filolar</span><span>ı</span><span>n</span><span>ı</span><span>n alg</span><span>ı</span><span>y</span><span>ı</span><span> nas</span><span>ı</span><span>l de</span><span>ğ</span><span>i</span><span>ş</span><span>tirece</span><span>ğ</span><span>ini kim tahmin edebilir?</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in 0.0001pt;\"><span>Yapay zeka ayn</span><span>ı</span><span> zamanda kapal</span><span>ı</span><span> kap</span><span>ı</span><span>lar ard</span><span>ı</span><span>nda bekleyen derin anlay</span><span>ış</span><span> dehas</span><span>ı</span><span> olarak s</span><span>ö</span><span>zde bir</span><span>&nbsp;“</span><span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.scientificamerican.com/article/demystifying-the-black-box-that-is-ai/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">kara kutu</span></a></span><span>”</span><span> da kullan</span><span>ı</span><span>r. Girdiyi ve </span><span>çı</span><span>kt</span><span>ı</span><span>y</span><span>ı</span><span> elbette biliyoruz, ancak yapay zekan</span><span>ı</span><span>n sonucuna ula</span><span>şı</span><span>rken ge</span><span>ç</span><span>ti</span><span>ğ</span><span>i s</span><span>ü</span><span>reci pek bilmeyiz. Altta yatan </span><span>ç</span><span>al</span><span>ış</span><span>ma gizlendi</span><span>ğ</span><span>inde (ve</span><span></span><span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://news.lenovo.com/how-inclusive-artificial-intelligence-is-disrupting-business-and-society/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">rastlant</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ı</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">sal </span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ö</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">nyarg</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ı</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">lar</span></a></span><span> i</span><span>ç</span><span>erebilece</span><span>ğ</span><span>inden) bir yan</span><span>ı</span><span>ta g</span><span>ü</span><span>venmek zor olabilir.</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>G</span><span>ü</span><span>ven duygusu </span><span>ö</span><span>n</span><span>ü</span><span>m</span><span>ü</span><span>zdeki on y</span><span>ı</span><span>l i</span><span>ç</span><span>inde artacakt</span><span>ı</span><span>r ancak bu kabul olmadan bile, i</span><span>ş</span><span>ler t</span><span>ı</span><span>p d</span><span>ü</span><span>nyas</span><span>ı</span><span>nda m</span><span>ü</span><span>mk</span><span>ü</span><span>n oldu</span><span>ğ</span><span>u kadar</span><span>ı</span><span>yla, b</span><span>ü</span><span>y</span><span>ü</span><span>k </span><span>ö</span><span>l</span><span>çü</span><span>de de</span><span>ğ</span><span>i</span><span>ş</span><span>ebilir.</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>Gen dizilimi kendi i</span><span>ç</span><span>inde bir devrimdir. Gen haritas</span><span>ı</span><span>n</span><span>ı</span><span>n </span><span>çı</span><span>kar</span><span>ı</span><span>lmas</span><span>ı</span><span> kal</span><span>ı</span><span>tsal ko</span><span>ş</span><span>ullar, hastal</span><span>ığ</span><span>a yatk</span><span>ı</span><span>nl</span><span>ı</span><span>k, tedaviye olas</span><span>ı</span><span> yan</span><span>ı</span><span>t gibi say</span><span>ı</span><span>s</span><span>ı</span><span>z bilgiye ula</span><span>şı</span><span>labilmesini sa</span><span>ğ</span><span>lar. Ancak bu i</span><span>ş</span><span>lem zaman al</span><span>ı</span><span>r ve y</span><span>ü</span><span>ksek performansl</span><span>ı</span><span> bilgisayarlar</span><span>ı</span><span>n kullan</span><span>ı</span><span>lmas</span><span>ı</span><span>n</span><span>ı</span><span> gerektirir.</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in 0.0001pt;\"><span>Lenovo, k</span><span>ı</span><span>sa s</span><span>ü</span><span>re </span><span>ö</span><span>nce</span><span></span><span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.hpcwire.com/2019/09/30/accelerating-high-performance-computing-hpc-for-population-level-genomics/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">gen dizilimini n</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ü</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">fus d</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ü</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">zeyine </span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ç</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ekme</span></a></span><span> </span><span>ç</span><span>al</span><span>ış</span><span>malar</span><span>ı</span><span>na ba</span><span>ş</span><span>lad</span><span>ı</span><span> ve 150 saatlik bilgi i</span><span>ş</span><span>lem s</span><span>ü</span><span>resini </span><span>ç</span><span>ok daha y</span><span>ö</span><span>netilebilir bir s</span><span>ü</span><span>reye indirdi. </span><span>Ç</span><span>o</span><span>ğ</span><span>undan daha kolay </span><span>ö</span><span>l</span><span>ç</span><span>eklenen </span><span>çö</span><span>z</span><span>ü</span><span>m </span><span>ö</span><span>nerilerinden biriyle tam bir gen dizilimi i</span><span>ç</span><span>in i</span><span>ş</span><span>lem yaln</span><span>ı</span><span>zca 5,5 saatte tamamlan</span><span>ı</span><span>yor. 10 y</span><span>ı</span><span>l i</span><span>ç</span><span>inde g</span><span>ö</span><span>rece</span><span>ğ</span><span>imiz yeniliklerle bu rakam</span><span>ı</span><span>n nas</span><span>ı</span><span>l de</span><span>ğ</span><span>i</span><span>ş</span><span>ece</span><span>ğ</span><span>ini d</span><span>üşü</span><span>n</span><span>ü</span><span>n.</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: center;\"><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"assets/build-in-contents/images/AI2.jpg\" style=\"height: 258px; width: 600px;\"></span></p> \n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><span>Lenovo'nun g</span><span>üç</span><span>l</span><span>ü</span><span> gen ara</span><span>ş</span><span>t</span><span>ı</span><span>rmalar</span><span>ı</span><span>na yard</span><span>ı</span><span>mc</span><span>ı</span><span> oldu</span><span>ğ</span><span>u Barcelona'daki bir kilisede bulunan MareNostrum s</span><span>ü</span><span>per bilgisayar</span><span>ı</span><span>.</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>“</span><span>Herkesin gen haritas</span><span>ı</span><span>n</span><span>ı</span><span> </span><span>çı</span><span>karabilsek ve tamamen ki</span><span>ş</span><span>iselle</span><span>ş</span><span>tirilmi</span><span>ş</span><span> bir t</span><span>ı</span><span>p hizmeti geli</span><span>ş</span><span>tirebilsek neler olur?</span><span>”</span><span> diyor Tease. </span><span>“</span><span>Yapay zeka ve HPC, hesaplama s</span><span>ü</span><span>resini talep </span><span>ü</span><span>zerine herkesin te</span><span>ş</span><span>his imkan</span><span>ı</span><span> bulabilece</span><span>ğ</span><span>i ve ideal, ki</span><span>ş</span><span>isel tedavisini belirleyebilece</span><span>ğ</span><span>i kadar azaltabilir mi?</span><span>”</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>Bu kadar b</span><span>ü</span><span>y</span><span>ü</span><span>k ad</span><span>ı</span><span>mlar</span><span>ı</span><span>n </span><span>ö</span><span>tesinde, Tease yapay zekan</span><span>ı</span><span>n kaliteli bak</span><span>ı</span><span>ma eri</span><span>ş</span><span>imi art</span><span>ı</span><span>rd</span><span>ığı</span><span> bir d</span><span>ü</span><span>nya hayal ediyor.</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>“</span><span>D</span><span>ü</span><span>nyan</span><span>ı</span><span>n herhangi bir yerindeki bir hasta, kan </span><span>ö</span><span>rne</span><span>ğ</span><span>ini ve ayr</span><span>ı</span><span>nt</span><span>ı</span><span>l</span><span>ı</span><span> biyometri verilerini payla</span><span>ş</span><span>abilir,</span><span>”</span><span> diyor. </span><span>“</span><span>Yapay zeka ilk analizi yapar, kal</span><span>ı</span><span>plar</span><span>ı</span><span> bulur, hastal</span><span>ığı</span><span> te</span><span>ş</span><span>his eder ve sonraki ad</span><span>ı</span><span>mlar</span><span>ı</span><span> </span><span>ö</span><span>nerir. Ard</span><span>ı</span><span>ndan, gerekirse, vaka do</span><span>ğ</span><span>ru uzmana y</span><span>ö</span><span>nlendirilir ve uzman</span><span>ı</span><span>n art</span><span>ı</span><span>k t</span><span>ü</span><span>m bu bilgiler elinin alt</span><span>ı</span><span>ndad</span><span>ı</span><span>r.</span><span>”</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in; text-align: center;\"><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"assets/build-in-contents/images/AI3.jpg\" style=\"height: 373px; width: 600px;\"></span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in 0.0001pt;\"><span>Buna, art</span><span>ı</span><span>r</span><span>ı</span><span>lm</span><span>ış</span><span> ger</span><span>ç</span><span>eklik ara</span><span>ç</span><span>lar</span><span>ı</span><span> ile yard</span><span>ı</span><span>m ve tedavi imkan</span><span>ı</span><span>n</span><span>ı</span><span> da ekleyin; maliyet d</span><span>üş</span><span>erken hem verimlilik hem de kalite y</span><span>ü</span><span>kselir. Bunun mevzuata nas</span><span>ı</span><span>l uyarlanaca</span><span>ğı</span><span>n</span><span>ı</span><span> g</span><span>ö</span><span>rmek ilgin</span><span>ç</span><span> ve</span><span></span><span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://hbr.org/2019/10/adopting-ai-in-health-care-will-be-slow-and-difficult\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">muhtemelen de s</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ı</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">k</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ı</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">nt</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ı</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">l</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ı</span></a></span><span> olacak, ancak h</span><span>ı</span><span>zl</span><span>ı</span><span> benimseme uygulamalar</span><span>ı</span><span> bize umut veriyor.</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin-top: 12pt;\"><span>Daha ayd</span><span>ı</span><span>nl</span><span>ı</span><span>k bir gelecekte, yapay zeka algoritmalar</span><span>ı</span><span>n</span><span>ı</span><span>n ancak mevcut veriler kadar g</span><span>üç</span><span>l</span><span>ü</span><span> oldu</span><span>ğ</span><span>unu d</span><span>üşü</span><span>n</span><span>ü</span><span>n. Makine </span><span>öğ</span><span>reniminin ba</span><span>ş</span><span>ar</span><span>ı</span><span>s</span><span>ı</span><span>n</span><span>ı</span><span>n temeli olan veriler, sa</span><span>ğ</span><span>l</span><span>ı</span><span>k hizmetlerinde b</span><span>ü</span><span>y</span><span>ü</span><span>k veri analizlerini</span><span></span><span><span style=\"color: blue;\">2025 y</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ı</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">l</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ı</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">nda yakla</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">şı</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">k 70 milyar ABD Dolar</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">ı</span></span><span> s</span><span>ı</span><span>n</span><span>ı</span><span>r</span><span>ı</span><span>na ta</span><span>şı</span><span>yacak. 2030 y</span><span>ı</span><span>l</span><span>ı</span><span>nda yapay zekan</span><span>ı</span><span>n hem hastalara hem de sa</span><span>ğ</span><span>l</span><span>ı</span><span>k uzmanlar</span><span>ı</span><span>na neler sunaca</span><span>ğı</span><span>n</span><span>ı</span><span> kim tahmin edebilir?</span></p> \n<p><span>&nbsp;</span></p>",
